<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>PSG College of Technology - Final Semester Internship</title>
  <style>
    @page {
      size: A4;
      margin: 12mm 16mm 10mm 16mm;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      color: #000;
      line-height: 1.3;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .page {
      width: 100%;
      page-break-after: always;
    }
    .page:last-child {
      page-break-after: avoid;
    }

    /* ── College header ── */
    .college-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }
    .college-name {
      font-size: 11pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .form-title {
      font-size: 10pt;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* ── Paragraphs ── */
    p {
      margin: 2px 0;
      font-size: 9.5pt;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    /* ── Tables ── */
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 3px 0;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
    }
    td, th {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 2px 4px;
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }
    th {
      font-weight: bold;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8pt;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
    .no-border td {
      border: none;
      padding: 0 2px;
    }

    /* ── Lists ── */
    ol {
      margin: 2px 0 2px 16px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    ol li {
      font-size: 9pt;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    ol.alpha {
      list-style-type: lower-alpha;
      margin-left: 20px;
    }

    /* ── Utility ── */
    .small   { font-size: 8pt; }
    .italic  { font-style: italic; }
    .bold    { font-weight: bold; }
    .center  { text-align: center; }
    .right   { text-align: right; }
    .underline { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── Sig lines ── */
    .sig-cell {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      border-top: 1px solid #000 !important;
      border-left: none !important;
      border-right: none !important;
      border-bottom: none !important;
      padding-top: 2px;
    }

    /* ── CGPA table ── */
    table.cgpa-table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 4px 0 5px 0;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
      width: 100%;
    }
    table.cgpa-table td,
    table.cgpa-table th {
      border: 1px solid #000;
      padding: 3px 6px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 8.5pt;
    }
    table.cgpa-table th {
      font-weight: bold;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
    }
    ol.undertaking li {
  line-height: 1.6;  /* change from 1.35 to 1.6 */
}

    .page-footer { text-align: center; font-size: 8.5pt; margin-top: 4px; }
    .pto { text-align: right; font-size: 8.5pt; font-weight: bold; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 1 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <div class="college-header">
    <div class="college-name">PSG COLLEGE OF TECHNOLOGY, COIMBATORE 641 004</div>
    <div class="form-title">Undertaking for Pursuing Internship in the Final Semester (UG/PG)</div>
  </div>

  <table class="no-border" style="margin:1px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:50%;">From</td>
      <td style="width:50%; text-align:right;"><strong>Date:</strong> {{currentDate}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p>{{student_name}}</p>
  <p>{{roll_number}}</p>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">To</p>
  <p>The Principal</p>
  <p>PSG College of Technology</p>
  <p>Coimbatore – 641004</p>

  <p style="margin-top:2px;">Through: THE HEAD OF THE DEPARTMENT, DEPARTMENT OF
    {{#if department}}{{department}}{{else}}------------------------------{{/if}}
  </p>

  <p style="margin-top:2px;">Dear Sir,</p>

  <p><strong>Sub:</strong> Undertaking while pursuing Internship/Project Work II in Industry / Institutions.</p>

  <p>I wish to inform that, I have been offered internship in the organization, details of which are provided below. The activities carried out during this internship will be adequate for completing Project Work II (Code………………..) as per the recommendations of the Guide and the project review committee.</p>

  <!-- Internship details table -->
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:26%;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:22%;">Guide from the Industry /<br>Institution with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:11%;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:11%;">Stipend<br>receivable (if any)</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:9%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:9%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td style="height:40px;">
          {{#if company_name}}<strong>{{company_name}}</strong><br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_address}}{{company_address}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if company_city}}{{company_city}}{{#if company_state}}, {{company_state}}{{/if}}{{/if}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{start_date}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{end_date}}</td>
        <td>
          {{#if guide_name_industry}}{{guide_name_industry}}<br>{{/if}}
          {{#if guide_contact}}{{guide_contact}}{{/if}}
        </td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{#if guide_name_dept}}{{guide_name_dept}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td style="text-align:center;">{{#if stipend_amount}}&#8377; {{stipend_amount}}{{else}}NIL{{/if}}</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

 

  <p>I request you to permit me to accept the offer of internship and provide attendance for the duration mentioned.</p>
  <p><strong>I hereby undertake the following.</strong></p>

  <ol>
    <li>I will be regular and sincere in carrying out my internship at the above organization and I will obey the Rules and Regulations of the organization.</li>
    <li>My attendance will be sent regularly to my department by the Industry / Institution.</li>
    <li>I will attend all the project work II reviews scheduled in the department and submit the report for my Project Work II on or before the deadline specified by the Department.</li>
    <li>I will update the guide in the college regularly through reports reviewed by the guide in the industry.</li>
    <li>*I have completed all course work except Project Work II to become eligible for the award of the Degree.</li>
    <li>*I have 1 / 2 final semester elective course/s for which I have registered along with other students. I will study the course/s under self study mode and I will appear for all CA Evaluation Tests/Tutorials in the above course/s.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed the offer letter for internship.</li>
    <li>I am aware of internship and conversion to full time offer and I will abide by the rules of Placement &amp; Training Office.</li>
    <li>I have enclosed my parent's permission letter to carry out the internship/Project work.</li>
    <li><sup>#</sup>I am not in receipt of any other scholarship/Stipend from the company (Applicable to PG AICTE GATE Scholarship / PG NON GATE State Government Scholarship Students).</li>
    <li>*If I intend to receive stipend from the company, I am aware that, I will not be eligible to receive the PG Scholarship receiving from AICTE / State Government during the period of my paid internship.</li>
  </ol>

  <p class="small" style="margin-top:3px;">*Strike out if not applicable.<br>
  <sup>#</sup> PG GATE Student has to produce a letter from the company in their letter head to this effect.</p>

  <p class="small italic" style="margin-top:2px;">Note: Do not edit the format</p>

  <!-- Page 1 sig row -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:10px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:34%;">Tutor/Programme Co-ordinator</td>
      <td style="width:22%; text-align:center;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:16%; text-align:center;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:28%; text-align:right;">(Signature of the Student)</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <div class="page-footer">Page 1/2</div>
  <div class="pto">(PTO)</div>

</div><!-- end page 1 -->


<!-- ═══════════════ PAGE 2 ═══════════════ -->
<div class="page">

  <!-- No college header on page 2 — starts directly with title -->
  <p class="center underline bold" style="font-size:10pt; margin:2px 0 6px 0;">Recommendation from the department</p>

  <p><strong>Academic details of the student:</strong></p>

  <!-- NAME, Roll Number, CGPA all on one line -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin:2px 0 4px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="width:8%;"><strong>NAME:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:30%;">{{student_name}}</td>
      <td style="width:16%; text-align:left;"><strong>Roll Number:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:20%;">{{roll_number}}</td>
      <td style="width:10%; text-align:left;"><strong>CGPA:</strong></td>
      <td style="width:16%;">{{#if cgpa_value}}{{cgpa_value}}{{/if}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Academic status table with 8 blank rows to match official -->
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:25%;">Number of Pending Redo courses with Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:25%;">Number of Pending RA courses with Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:30%;">Pending Courses of current semester with Course Code &amp; Title</th>
        <th style="width:20%;">REMARKS</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:22px;">
        <td>{{#if redo_courses}}{{redo_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{#if ra_courses}}{{ra_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td>{{#if pending_courses}}{{pending_courses}}{{/if}}</td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
      <tr style="height:22px;"><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">The work assigned by the industry / institution <strong>meets</strong> the academic standards for Project Work II.<br>
  This student has not accepted any other internship.</p>

  <p style="margin-top:3px; font-size:8.8pt;">*This student has accepted another internship but has declined the same due to academic / health / financial reasons. The company / institution is informed of his inability to accept the offer through letter/email. The details of the organization is given below.</p>

  <!-- Declined internship table -->
  <table style="margin-top:3px;">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:28%;">Name &amp; Address of the<br>Industry / Institution</th>
        <th colspan="2">Internship Period</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:25%;">Guide from the Industry /<br>institution with contact details</th>
        <th rowspan="2" style="width:13%;">Guide in the<br>department</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:11%;">From (Date)</th>
        <th style="width:11%;">To (Date)</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr style="height:35px;">
        <td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p style="margin-top:4px;">This student can be permitted to accept the internship and complete Project Work II within the specified time period.</p>

  <!-- Sig row 1 -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:18px;">
    <tr>
      <td  style="width:24%;">Tutor/Programme Coordinator</td>
      <td style="width:2%;"></td>
      <td  style="width:16%;">Guide</td>
      <td style="width:2%; "></td>
      <td  style="width:16%;">HoD</td>
      <td style="width:2%; "></td>
      <td  style="width:38%;">Dean, Placement &amp; Training</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <!-- Sig row 2 -->
  <table class="no-border" style="margin-top:22px;">
    <tr>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:40%;">Dean - Academic</td>
      <td style="width:10%; border:none;"></td>
      <td class="sig-cell" style="width:50%;">Principal</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <p class="small" style="margin-top:5px;">*Strike out if not applicable.</p>

  <!-- NOTE — normal document flow, not fixed -->
  <div style="margin-top:8px; font-size:8.5pt; line-height:1.3;">
    <strong>NOTE:</strong>
    <ol style="margin: 2px 0 0 16px;">
      <li style="font-size:8.5pt;">Original Form shall be submitted to <strong>Placement Office</strong></li>
      <li style="font-size:8.5pt;">Photo copies shall be submitted to
        <ol class="alpha">
          <li style="font-size:8.5pt;">Academic section</li>
          <li style="font-size:8.5pt;">Concerned Department</li>
        </ol>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div class="page-footer" style="margin-top:6px;">Page 2/2</div>

</div><!-- end page 2 -->

</body>
</html>
